on you, because I'm telling you,

11:31.474 --> 11:33.243
if you make the wrong
decision too early,

11:33.276 --> 11:34.911
then you could end up
tethered to someone

11:34.945 --> 11:37.680
for the rest of your life
who drives you

11:37.713 --> 11:39.715
