12:38.942 --> 12:42.812
-Mm.
-He was talking
about love, heartbreak.

12:42.845 --> 12:46.216
Well, maybe that's a good thing.
He trying to bond with you.

12:46.249 --> 12:49.419
Nah.
Ain't sound like a good thing.

12:49.452 --> 12:52.088
-Sound like he was fucked up.
-Mm.

12:54.124 --> 12:57.593
Listen, Franklin,
I know you got a lot of shit

12:57.627 --> 13:00.430
