and sort through,

13:00.463 --> 13:03.066
but Leon and Jerome,
they need to know the truth

13:03.099 --> 13:05.868
-about what we dealing with.
-I know.

13:05.902 --> 13:07.870
And I'm-a tell them, too.

13:07.904 --> 13:10.040
I'm-a tell them.

13:10.073 --> 13:11.674
(sighs)

13:11.707 --> 13:13.576
Just got to find
the right time, you know?

13:13.609 --> 13:16.046
You talking about
maybe needing to run.

13:16.079 --> 13:18.348
This is the time.

13:18.381 --> 13:20.250
Besides, I'm tired
of trying to hide shit

13:20.283 --> 13:22.252
-from my man.
-(pager beeping)

13:22.285 --> 13:24.287
-They found her.
-Mel?

13:24.320 --> 13:26.122
