13:49.745 --> 13:50.913
Just one.

13:50.947 --> 13:52.482
Just one rock.

13:52.515 --> 13:54.384
What...? Wh...?

13:54.417 --> 13:56.819
(sighs) Fuck!

13:56.852 --> 13:58.721
