14:09.299 --> 14:12.235
I'm telling you this
as somebody who cares about you:

14:12.268 --> 14:13.936
You got to stop.

14:13.970 --> 14:15.638
* Just a flick of his wrist... *

14:15.671 --> 14:16.839
Okay?

14:16.872 --> 14:19.309
