14:36.993 --> 14:39.329
-I don't know if I can.
-You can.

14:39.362 --> 14:41.764
You can,
'cause I'll take you home.

14:41.797 --> 14:43.666
Okay? We'll get you out.

14:43.699 --> 14:46.369
-Okay?
-Okay.

14:46.402 --> 14:49.105
Good.
Well, let's get out of here.

14:49.139 --> 14:51.007
-(Franklin grunts)
-(laughter)

14:51.041 --> 14:52.608
