your own business

19:00.222 --> 19:01.457
and they came up on you?

19:01.491 --> 19:02.958
Nah, man, we rolled up on them,

19:02.992 --> 19:04.927
'cause they were selling
in our territory.

19:04.960 --> 19:06.429
Come on, man,
ain't you been listening?

19:06.462 --> 19:08.464
Nigga, what's the move?
Who we gonna hit first?

19:08.498 --> 19:11.200
Ain't gonna be no retaliation
till I talk to Saint.

19:11.233 --> 19:13.903
Man, fuck talking.
That time is done.

19:13.936 --> 19:15.738
I don't eat no ass,

19:15.771 --> 19:18.073
I don't cuss in front
of my little sisters,

19:18.107 --> 19:19.775
and I don't go to war

19:19.809 --> 19:22.077
'cause one of mine's
got some cuts and bruises.

19:22.111 --> 19:24.280
-This some bullshit.
-No, this some Leon.

19:24.314 --> 19:27.383
See, your problem is,
you got tunnel vision.

19:27.417 --> 19:30.720
Luckily, I can see
the whole field.

19:30.753 --> 19:32.722
Somebody get
this nigga some ice.

19:32.755 --> 19:34.690
That shit fucked up.

